isis.stitle: TSI 95-12-18R - Release 1993/1994/1995 Model Year "Engine Data" And "Fuel Injection Pump Calibration Data" For Service To DT-408/466 And The International® 530 Diesel Engines

subjectgroup.subject: Release 1993/1994/1995 Model Year "Engine Data" And "Fuel Injection Pump Calibration Data" For Service To DT-408/466 And The International® 530 Diesel Engines

geninfo.title: Addendum No. 1
geninfo.para: This TSI incorporates Addendum No. 1, which consists of the following information:
The following table specifies the equipment that is required to calibrate the Robert Bosch pump models P-3000 and P-7100 as specified for the DT 408, DT 466 and the International 530 diesel engines.
The calibration fluid required is I.S.O. 4113, equivalent to Viscor 1487.

para.emph: Calibrating Nozzle (Bosch P/N) Type and Orifice Plate Size Valve Opening Pressure

entry.para: Injection Line Bosch P/N and Size
